   161	
   162	## C9 — Mount mid-transition (existing and fresh nodes)
   163	
   164	Schedule: transition k writes atoms; while k is pending/rendering, a
   165	component mounts and reads (a) an existing computed over k-touched atoms,
   166	(b) a **freshly created** node (`useComputed` created during this render)
